 <i>Team Nankatsu goes</i>
 <i>up against Team Musashi,</i>

00:00:12.514 --> 00:00:15.482 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>lead by Jun Misugi,</i>
 <i>the prince of the pitch.</i>

00:00:15.517 --> 00:00:18.352 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Using his prowess</i>
 <i>and technique in soccer,</i>

00:00:18.385 --> 00:00:20.989 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>the prince ensnares</i>
 <i>Tsubasa in a trap.</i>

00:00:21.021 --> 00:00:23.023 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Every play leaves</i>
 <i>Tsubasa offside,</i>

00:00:23.056 --> 00:00:25.058 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>demoralizing the captain</i>
 <i>and his team.</i>

00:00:25.092 --> 00:00:27.461 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Every attempt to score</i>
 <i>is nulled.</i>

00:00:27.494 --> 00:00:29.697 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa is</i>
 <i>offside again!</i>

00:00:31.098 --> 00:00:32.165 position:41% line:83% align:start
[gasp]
[ann] <i>Once more,</i>

00:00:32.199 --> 00:00:33.267 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>he's offside.</i>

00:00:33.300 --> 00:00:34.569 position:33% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>Before</i>
 <i>the terrible strategy</i>

00:00:34.602 --> 00:00:37.104 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>from team Musashi,</i>
 <i>Tsubasa lost his confidence</i>

00:00:37.137 --> 00:00:40.274 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and let the situation</i>
 <i>get worse as his doubt grew.</i>

00:00:40.307 --> 00:00:43.377 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa] <i>His style of play</i>
 <i>is way better than mine.</i>

00:00:43.410 --> 00:00:44.812 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>And on top of that, Jun...</i>

00:00:44.846 --> 00:00:48.750 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>has team members that are</i>
 <i>almost as skillful as he is.</i>

00:00:48.783 --> 00:00:49.984 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Jun...</i>

00:00:50.018 --> 00:00:51.886 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>even with your heart</i>
 <i>condition affecting you,</i>

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:53.387 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>you stand your ground.</i>

00:00:54.622 --> 00:00:55.690 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>No...</i>

00:00:55.723 --> 00:00:57.090 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>I won't ever beat you.</i>

00:00:57.926 --> 00:01:00.160 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Jun, I can't fight you</i>
 <i>head on.</i>

00:01:00.193 --> 00:01:01.596 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Jun]
 <i>What're you doing, Tsubasa?</i>

00:01:01.629 --> 00:01:04.999 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>You promised to face me</i>
 <i>giving it your all.</i>

00:01:05.033 --> 00:01:06.333 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>I can't do it.</i>

00:01:06.366 --> 00:01:08.002 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Jun] <i>What's wrong with you,</i>
 <i>Tsubasa?</i>

00:01:08.036 --> 00:01:09.303 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm waiting for you.</i>

00:01:09.336 --> 00:01:11.371 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>Come here.</i>
 <i>Try to stop me if you can.</i>

00:01:11.405 --> 00:01:13.073 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>I'm sorry, I can't do it.</i>

00:01:14.676 --> 00:01:15.643 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:01:16.978 --> 00:01:18.445 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm disappointed.</i>

00:01:21.148 --> 00:01:23.116 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And the ball</i>
 <i>hits the net!</i>

00:01:23.150 --> 00:01:24.686 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Musashi is</i>
 <i>now winning.</i>

00:01:24.719 --> 00:01:27.454 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>We're excited to see</i>
 <i>what'll happen now.</i>

00:01:27.487 --> 00:01:29.057 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Jun] Listen up,
attack them with

00:01:29.089 --> 00:01:30.792 position:19% line:83% align:start
every ounce of strength
you have.

00:01:30.825 --> 00:01:31.960 position:16% line:89% align:start
Destroy what little pride

00:01:31.993 --> 00:01:34.494 position:24% line:83% align:start
that mediocre team
has left in them.

00:01:34.529 --> 00:01:35.530 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:03:21.803 --> 00:03:25.506 position:24% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>Episode 21:</i>
 <i>The Ace of Glass.</i>

00:03:26.941 --> 00:03:28.375 position:21% line:89% align:start
You get up, Tsubasa!

00:03:28.408 --> 00:03:30.545 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Uh...
-[Genzo] You need to get up.

00:03:30.578 --> 00:03:31.913 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:03:33.213 --> 00:03:35.116 position:16% line:83% align:start
-What's Genzo doing here?
-What's Genzo doing here?

00:03:35.149 --> 00:03:35.683 position:21% line:89% align:start
Genzo Wakabayashi...

00:03:36.818 --> 00:03:40.121 position:19% line:83% align:start
Did you already forget
the promise you made to me?

00:03:40.154 --> 00:03:41.856 position:24% line:83% align:start
You said you'd win
every single match

00:03:41.889 --> 00:03:43.091 position:27% line:89% align:start
until the finals.

00:03:43.124 --> 00:03:44.859 position:19% line:89% align:start
You're the captain now.

00:03:44.892 --> 00:03:45.993 position:19% line:89% align:start
Will you let them down?

00:03:46.027 --> 00:03:47.895 position:21% line:83% align:start
Your team needs you.
Answer me.

00:03:47.929 --> 00:03:49.997 position:27% line:83% align:start
So now you won't
talk either?

00:03:50.031 --> 00:03:52.734 position:44% line:83% align:start
Uh...
This is hard, Genzo.

00:03:52.767 --> 00:03:54.769 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Genzo] Don't tell me
I spent all this time

00:03:54.802 --> 00:03:56.104 position:16% line:89% align:start
recovering for no reason.

00:03:56.137 --> 00:03:57.672 position:24% line:89% align:start
Answer me, Tsubasa.

00:03:57.705 --> 00:03:59.907 position:19% line:83% align:start
Are you willing to let
everybody down?

00:03:59.941 --> 00:04:00.908 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uhh...

00:04:00.942 --> 00:04:03.243 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Roberto] Listen to
your teammate, Tsubasa.

00:04:03.276 --> 00:04:04.011 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-[Roberto] Tell me you're

00:04:04.045 --> 00:04:05.813 position:21% line:89% align:start
you're not giving up.

00:04:05.847 --> 00:04:09.016 position:16% line:83% align:start
Or maybe...you don't want
to go to Brazil anymore?

00:04:09.050 --> 00:04:10.518 position:30% line:89% align:start
Answer us now.

00:04:10.551 --> 00:04:11.451 position:35% line:89% align:start
Roberto...

00:04:11.886 --> 00:04:12.820 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:04:12.854 --> 00:04:14.354 position:24% line:83% align:start
I won't forgive you
if you don't play like

00:04:14.387 --> 00:04:16.023 position:27% line:89% align:start
your usual self.

00:04:16.057 --> 00:04:17.457 position:24% line:89% align:start
You need to get up.

00:04:17.491 --> 00:04:19.292 position:30% line:83% align:start
You need to win
today's match.

00:04:19.326 --> 00:04:20.895 position:16% line:89% align:start
Do it for everyone here.

00:04:20.928 --> 00:04:22.395 position:41% line:83% align:start
[gasp]
Hmm...

00:04:23.765 --> 00:04:24.699 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
Tsubasa...

00:04:24.732 --> 00:04:26.033 position:21% line:83% align:start
do you still remember
the day

00:04:26.067 --> 00:04:27.300 position:19% line:89% align:start
we met playing soccer?

00:04:28.169 --> 00:04:29.704 position:16% line:89% align:start
You and I were rivals...

00:04:29.737 --> 00:04:30.738 position:24% line:89% align:start
and that rivalry...

00:04:30.772 --> 00:04:33.306 position:21% line:83% align:start
is what made us play
with everything we had

00:04:33.340 --> 00:04:34.609 position:30% line:89% align:start
until the end.

00:04:34.642 --> 00:04:36.844 position:27% line:83% align:start
We share the same
fighting spirit.

00:04:38.112 --> 00:04:38.679 position:27% line:89% align:start
Get the hell up.

00:04:39.580 --> 00:04:42.016 position:21% line:83% align:start
We still have a goal
we need to reach.

00:04:42.049 --> 00:04:44.252 position:30% line:83% align:start
To beat Kojiro
in the finals.

00:04:44.317 --> 00:04:45.485 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:47.622 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Genzo] I've trained hard,
just like you have.

00:04:47.655 --> 00:04:48.623 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:04:48.656 --> 00:04:52.093 position:27% line:83% align:start
I won't allow you
to ruin everybody's dreams.

00:04:52.126 --> 00:04:54.494 position:27% line:83% align:start
You're not alone.
We're all here with you.

00:04:54.529 --> 00:04:54.829 position:38% line:89% align:start
Wake up.

00:04:55.630 --> 00:04:56.898 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Uh...
-[Taro] You should listen

00:04:56.931 --> 00:04:58.331 position:35% line:83% align:start
-to Genzo.
-Huh?

00:04:58.365 --> 00:04:59.534 position:21% line:89% align:start
Jun is right as well.

00:04:59.567 --> 00:05:00.768 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's waiting for you
to play,

00:05:00.802 --> 00:05:03.571 position:30% line:83% align:start
giving your all
like always have, Tsubasa.

00:05:03.604 --> 00:05:03.838 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:05:04.672 --> 00:05:07.108 position:19% line:83% align:start
You can't let him down
like this.

00:05:07.141 --> 00:05:08.576 position:19% line:83% align:start
Nor can you disappoint
the team

00:05:08.609 --> 00:05:10.778 position:27% line:83% align:start
that's been there
by your side.

00:05:10.812 --> 00:05:12.412 position:16% line:83% align:start
We're all counting on you
to make it

00:05:12.445 --> 00:05:14.148 position:33% line:83% align:start
to the finals
of the tournament.

00:05:14.182 --> 00:05:15.216 position:27% line:83% align:start
And you shouldn't
forget that...

00:05:15.249 --> 00:05:16.884 position:10% line:89% align:start
the ball is our best friend.

00:05:16.918 --> 00:05:17.919 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:05:20.922 --> 00:05:22.890 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:05:30.998 --> 00:05:32.365 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:05:32.399 --> 00:05:33.668 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's the spirit.

00:05:33.701 --> 00:05:34.669 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa.

00:05:35.002 --> 00:05:36.336 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:05:36.369 --> 00:05:37.572 position:30% line:89% align:start
Do it, Tsubasa.

00:05:41.309 --> 00:05:42.877 position:10% line:89% align:start
Please forgive me, you guys.

00:05:42.910 --> 00:05:46.080 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry for the way I've
been playing up until now.

00:05:46.113 --> 00:05:47.849 position:27% line:83% align:start
I forgot how much
this opportunity

00:05:47.882 --> 00:05:48.983 position:19% line:89% align:start
really means everyone.

00:05:49.851 --> 00:05:51.118 position:21% line:89% align:start
And to me as well...

00:05:51.152 --> 00:05:53.020 position:10% line:89% align:start
This match means everything.

00:05:53.921 --> 00:05:55.089 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm going to play...

00:05:56.389 --> 00:05:57.490 position:21% line:89% align:start
But this time around,

00:05:57.525 --> 00:05:59.927 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'm not holding
anything back anymore.

00:05:59.961 --> 00:06:00.728 position:33% line:89% align:start
You said it.

00:06:00.761 --> 00:06:02.362 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's the Tsubasa
I know and love.

00:06:02.395 --> 00:06:03.865 position:27% line:83% align:start
-We're gonna win.
-Let's win this.

00:06:03.898 --> 00:06:05.600 position:16% line:83% align:start
They're not gonna beat us
that easily.

00:06:05.633 --> 00:06:08.269 position:13% line:83% align:start
From now on, they're going
to see the real Nankatsu.

00:06:08.302 --> 00:06:09.469 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>If it wasn't for you,</i>

00:06:09.503 --> 00:06:12.139 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I wouldn't be able to play</i>
 <i>giving my all.</i>

00:06:12.173 --> 00:06:13.140 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
 <i>Tsubasa.</i>

00:06:13.174 --> 00:06:15.943 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chatter]

00:06:15.977 --> 00:06:18.279 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>In the end, it looks like</i>
 <i>you decided to get serious.</i>

00:06:18.312 --> 00:06:19.280 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm glad.</i>

00:06:19.313 --> 00:06:20.615 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>The game</i>
 <i>is still going</i>

00:06:20.648 --> 00:06:23.150 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and team Nankatsu will</i>
 <i>start the match up again.</i>

00:06:23.184 --> 00:06:24.619 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>With a few minutes</i>
 <i>on the clock,</i>

00:06:24.652 --> 00:06:26.654 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>it'll be hard for them</i>
 <i>to tie the score.</i>

00:06:26.687 --> 00:06:28.256 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Let's see if they can</i>
 <i>tie the match</i>

00:06:28.289 --> 00:06:29.790 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>with so little time</i>
 <i>left on the clock.</i>

00:06:29.824 --> 00:06:31.491 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[cheering]
-You can do it, Tsubasa.

00:06:31.525 --> 00:06:33.928 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Cheer up, Nankatsu.
-You can do it!

00:06:33.961 --> 00:06:34.862 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:06:34.896 --> 00:06:37.198 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And now,</i>
 <i>Nankatsu has the ball.</i>

00:06:37.231 --> 00:06:38.699 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's our turn, Musashi.

00:06:38.733 --> 00:06:41.135 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yeah, we're right
behind you, Tsubasa.

00:06:41.168 --> 00:06:42.303 position:16% line:83% align:start
I won't let you through.
[grunt]

00:06:42.336 --> 00:06:43.938 position:35% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Whoa,</i>
 <i>it looks like Tsubasa</i>

00:06:43.971 --> 00:06:45.139 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>has finally woken up</i>

00:06:45.172 --> 00:06:46.140 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>and is playing</i>
 <i>like always.</i>

00:06:46.173 --> 00:06:47.375 position:30% line:89% align:start
Good, Tsubasa.

00:06:47.407 --> 00:06:48.643 position:44% line:89% align:start
Whoa!

00:06:48.676 --> 00:06:51.812 position:38% line:83% align:start
[panting]
[grunting]

00:06:51.846 --> 00:06:53.514 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's right, Tsubasa,
keep on going.

00:06:53.547 --> 00:06:54.782 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Roberto]
 <i>Good, Tsubasa.</i>

00:06:54.815 --> 00:06:57.518 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>You finally got</i>
 <i>your fighting spirit back.</i>

00:06:57.551 --> 00:07:00.354 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Your talent was never</i>
 <i>overshadowed by Jun...</i>

00:07:00.388 --> 00:07:02.455 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>You're a worthy opponent.</i>

00:07:02.489 --> 00:07:03.925 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>You have to face him.</i>

00:07:03.958 --> 00:07:06.459 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Go and show him</i>
 <i>what you're made of.</i>

00:07:06.493 --> 00:07:07.995 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>You can do it, Captain.</i>

00:07:08.029 --> 00:07:08.495 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:07:09.496 --> 00:07:11.332 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And Tsubasa</i>
 <i>evades the slide tackle</i>

00:07:11.365 --> 00:07:12.366 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>with a huge leap.</i>

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:13.801 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Jun]
 <i>Despite the pouring rain,</i>

00:07:13.834 --> 00:07:16.170 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa isn't faced</i>
 <i>by anything.</i>

00:07:16.203 --> 00:07:18.438 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>His balance is</i>
 <i>simply perfect.</i>

00:07:18.471 --> 00:07:22.143 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>That's the Tsubasa I've</i>
 <i>been dying to challenge.</i>

00:07:22.176 --> 00:07:23.110 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:23.144 --> 00:07:24.045 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's all yours, Taro.

00:07:24.078 --> 00:07:25.046 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:07:25.913 --> 00:07:26.614 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:26.647 --> 00:07:27.748 position:33% line:83% align:start
-What just--?
-What just--?

00:07:27.782 --> 00:07:29.750 position:35% line:83% align:start
It's yours.
Now it's our turn, Tsubasa.

00:07:29.784 --> 00:07:30.785 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:33.486 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>What an excellent</i>

00:07:33.521 --> 00:07:35.022 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>series of passes</i>
 <i>from the famous</i>

00:07:35.056 --> 00:07:35.790 position:33% line:83% align:start
- <i>golden duo.</i>
-[laugh]

00:07:35.823 --> 00:07:36.857 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>It looks like</i>
-[cheering]

00:07:36.891 --> 00:07:38.125 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>Nankatsu's golden duo</i>
-Good job.

00:07:38.159 --> 00:07:39.393 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>is back in business.</i>
-You're our golden duo.

00:07:39.427 --> 00:07:40.594 position:30% line:89% align:start
You can do it.

00:07:40.628 --> 00:07:41.829 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But Jun Misugi</i>
 <i>is waiting for them</i>

00:07:41.862 --> 00:07:43.898 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>in front of the goal</i>
 <i>to put a stop to them.</i>

00:07:43.931 --> 00:07:45.232 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa] <i>I will admit that</i>
 <i>your technique</i>

00:07:45.266 --> 00:07:46.600 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>is way better than mine...</i>

00:07:46.634 --> 00:07:49.637 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>but you won't beat me</i>
 <i>in fighting spirit.</i>

00:07:49.670 --> 00:07:51.439 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Jun]
 <i>Come, now or never.</i>

00:07:51.471 --> 00:07:53.574 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Finally, this is our battle.</i>

00:07:53.607 --> 00:07:55.309 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[Jun] Yeah!
-[Tsubasa] Yeah!

00:07:55.343 --> 00:07:56.744 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:56.777 --> 00:07:58.846 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

