 <i>with ten minutes left</i>
 <i>for the match to end.</i>

00:10:07.808 --> 00:10:09.643 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu still has</i>
 <i>an opportunity.</i>

00:10:09.677 --> 00:10:11.078 position:21% line:89% align:start
You did a great job.

00:10:11.112 --> 00:10:12.847 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Great job, Tsubasa.</i>

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:14.949 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Without a doubt,</i>
 <i>Jun Misugi's technique</i>

00:10:14.982 --> 00:10:17.552 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>makes him a true prodigy</i>
 <i>of the game.</i>

00:10:17.586 --> 00:10:18.719 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>But unlike you,</i>

