What's he doing?

00:13:50.699 --> 00:13:52.066 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa is</i>
 <i>getting ready to shoot</i>

00:13:52.099 --> 00:13:53.400 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>from that angle and...</i>

00:13:53.434 --> 00:13:54.435 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:13:55.336 --> 00:13:56.136 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scream]

00:13:56.170 --> 00:13:58.172 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>he ties the match!</i>

00:13:58.205 --> 00:13:59.641 position:16% line:83% align:start
- <i>Tsubasa used the water</i>
-[cheering]

00:13:59.674 --> 00:14:03.077 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>to slide and make that</i>
 <i>spectacular shot from below!</i>

00:14:03.110 --> 00:14:04.945 position:10% line:83% align:start
-We actually tied the match.
-[laughing]

00:14:04.978 --> 00:14:06.715 position:21% line:89% align:start
You did it, Tsubasa.

00:14:06.748 --> 00:14:09.316 position:19% line:83% align:start
That play was amazing.
Congratulations.

00:14:09.350 --> 00:14:11.285 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:14:11.318 --> 00:14:12.286 position:44% line:83% align:start
Huh?
[gasps]

00:14:12.319 --> 00:14:14.988 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But what's</i>
 <i>happening over here?</i>

00:14:15.022 --> 00:14:16.857 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Musashi's captain,</i>
 <i>Jun Misugi,</i>

00:14:16.890 --> 00:14:19.226 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>is on the ground with</i>
 <i>his hand over his chest.</i>

00:14:19.259 --> 00:14:20.327 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>What could be wrong</i>
 <i>with him?</i>

00:14:20.361 --> 00:14:21.295 position:33% line:89% align:start
Are you okay?

00:14:21.328 --> 00:14:22.329 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:14:22.363 --> 00:14:23.565 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Captain!
-Captain!

00:14:23.598 --> 00:14:24.498 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Jun!
-Jun!

00:14:24.532 --> 00:14:26.601 position:47% line:83% align:start
Oh!
Let me help him.

00:14:26.634 --> 00:14:27.569 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh-uh.

00:14:28.402 --> 00:14:29.571 position:19% line:89% align:start
We need to sub him out.

00:14:29.604 --> 00:14:31.171 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Go in, Kojima.
-Yes.

00:14:31.205 --> 00:14:32.940 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[Jun] Wait a second.
-Huh?

00:14:32.973 --> 00:14:34.475 position:27% line:89% align:start
Just a bit more.

00:14:34.509 --> 00:14:36.176 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
I'm begging you...

00:14:36.210 --> 00:14:37.077 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:14:37.111 --> 00:14:39.246 position:33% line:83% align:start
You promised
to let me play...

00:14:39.279 --> 00:14:40.381 position:27% line:89% align:start
the whole match.

00:14:40.414 --> 00:14:41.783 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm begging you...

00:14:41.816 --> 00:14:44.251 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't want to abandon
my teammates.

00:14:44.284 --> 00:14:45.386 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, Jun...

00:14:45.419 --> 00:14:45.620 position:33% line:89% align:start
Everybody...

00:14:46.821 --> 00:14:49.423 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm really sorry for
keeping this from you...

00:14:49.456 --> 00:14:50.891 position:21% line:89% align:start
but as you can see...

00:14:50.924 --> 00:14:52.292 position:19% line:89% align:start
it's a serious problem.

00:14:52.326 --> 00:14:53.460 position:41% line:83% align:start
-What?
-What?

00:14:53.494 --> 00:14:57.197 position:13% line:83% align:start
My heart condition doesn't
let me play for a long time.

00:14:57.231 --> 00:14:59.466 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's why this match
is different.

00:14:59.500 --> 00:15:02.169 position:13% line:83% align:start
Team Nankatsu isn't a team
we would be able to defeat

00:15:02.202 --> 00:15:04.204 position:27% line:83% align:start
if I didn't play
the whole match.

00:15:04.238 --> 00:15:06.240 position:35% line:83% align:start
That's why
I've already decided.

00:15:06.273 --> 00:15:09.677 position:13% line:83% align:start
This will be the last match
I play in my whole life.

00:15:09.711 --> 00:15:11.780 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm begging all of you
to please...

00:15:11.813 --> 00:15:13.247 position:10% line:89% align:start
play with all your strength,

00:15:13.280 --> 00:15:15.717 position:19% line:83% align:start
as if it were the last
soccer match of your lives.

00:15:15.750 --> 00:15:17.184 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Captain...
-Captain...

00:15:17.217 --> 00:15:20.421 position:13% line:83% align:start
I want you to play with me
until the very end.

00:15:20.454 --> 00:15:20.622 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:15:21.823 --> 00:15:24.425 position:10% line:83% align:start
our battle is far from over,
you hear that?

00:15:24.458 --> 00:15:25.459 position:38% line:89% align:start
Misugi...

00:15:25.492 --> 00:15:27.127 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Mr. Misugi] That's what
I want to hear, Son.

00:15:27.161 --> 00:15:28.328 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Don't give up.
-Huh?

00:15:29.196 --> 00:15:31.231 position:27% line:83% align:start
We know how much
you love this sport.

00:15:31.265 --> 00:15:33.233 position:24% line:83% align:start
Don't let anything
take away that passion.

00:15:33.267 --> 00:15:35.936 position:24% line:83% align:start
You have to give it
your all until the end.

00:15:35.969 --> 00:15:37.237 position:30% line:89% align:start
Thanks, Dad...

00:15:37.271 --> 00:15:39.607 position:21% line:83% align:start
Ryota, we'll hold off
the substitution.

00:15:39.641 --> 00:15:40.407 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:15:40.441 --> 00:15:41.341 position:41% line:89% align:start
Misugi!

00:15:41.375 --> 00:15:43.845 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm leaving this match
in your hands now.

00:15:43.878 --> 00:15:45.045 position:33% line:89% align:start
Coach Isao...

00:15:45.078 --> 00:15:46.380 position:16% line:89% align:start
Let's win this, Captain.

00:15:46.413 --> 00:15:49.016 position:19% line:83% align:start
We'll follow you until
the end, Captain.

00:15:49.049 --> 00:15:50.117 position:24% line:89% align:start
Thank you, guys...

00:15:50.150 --> 00:15:52.419 position:44% line:83% align:start
What?
He has a heart condition?

00:15:52.453 --> 00:15:53.153 position:30% line:89% align:start
Sounds serious.

00:15:54.154 --> 00:15:56.791 position:21% line:83% align:start
Everybody, I want you
to give it your all.

00:15:56.825 --> 00:15:57.892 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:15:57.926 --> 00:16:00.227 position:16% line:83% align:start
We can't let Misugi down
by pitying him.

00:16:00.260 --> 00:16:01.763 position:21% line:83% align:start
We have to play with
everything we've got

00:16:01.796 --> 00:16:02.496 position:33% line:89% align:start
'til the end.

00:16:02.530 --> 00:16:03.565 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa...</i>

00:16:03.598 --> 00:16:06.033 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>So that means you knew</i>
 <i>about his heart problem?</i>

00:16:06.066 --> 00:16:07.434 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>This whole time you knew?</i>

00:16:08.435 --> 00:16:10.204 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>There is only</i>
 <i>seven minutes left</i>

00:16:10.237 --> 00:16:11.371 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>for the semifinals</i>
 <i>to finish</i>

00:16:11.405 --> 00:16:13.207 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the scoreboard</i>
 <i>is still tied.</i>

00:16:13.240 --> 00:16:14.341 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Despite the pain</i>
 <i>he's feeling,</i>

00:16:14.374 --> 00:16:16.109 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>captain Jun Misugi</i>
 <i>is in position</i>

00:16:16.143 --> 00:16:17.846 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>with his hand</i>
 <i>over his chest.</i>

00:16:17.879 --> 00:16:19.112 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>We hope</i>
 <i>it's nothing serious.</i>

00:16:19.146 --> 00:16:21.516 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Yayoi] <i>Captain...</i>
-[whistle]

00:16:21.549 --> 00:16:23.283 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>This match is</i>
 <i>burning with passion</i>

00:16:23.317 --> 00:16:25.052 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>and Musashi has the ball.</i>

00:16:25.085 --> 00:16:27.555 position:13% line:83% align:start
We have to help the captain
and give our best.

00:16:27.589 --> 00:16:28.756 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:16:28.790 --> 00:16:29.990 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Misugi...</i>

00:16:30.491 --> 00:16:32.827 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:16:32.861 --> 00:16:34.127 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa has</i>
 <i>control of the ball</i>

00:16:34.161 --> 00:16:36.129 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and he is running to</i>
 <i>the opponent's goal.</i>

00:16:36.163 --> 00:16:37.699 position:38% line:83% align:start
Perfect.
It's our opportunity.

00:16:37.732 --> 00:16:38.800 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Keep going!
-Yeah!

00:16:38.833 --> 00:16:40.100 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But the prince</i>
 <i>of the pitch</i>

00:16:40.133 --> 00:16:42.369 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>is waiting for Tsubasa</i>
 <i>in the penalty area.</i>

00:16:42.402 --> 00:16:44.404 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:16:44.438 --> 00:16:45.773 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Misugi...</i>

00:16:45.807 --> 00:16:47.241 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>if you weren't sick...</i>

00:16:47.274 --> 00:16:50.277 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>none of us would have</i>
 <i>a chance of beating you.</i>

00:16:50.310 --> 00:16:52.145 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:16:52.179 --> 00:16:55.884 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I won't lose this match,</i>
 <i>because I too love soccer.</i>

00:16:55.917 --> 00:16:57.952 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>More than anything</i>
 <i>in the world.</i>

00:16:57.986 --> 00:16:59.219 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>And I won't lose to anyone.</i>

00:17:00.287 --> 00:17:02.891 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Incredible,</i>
 <i>Misugi couldn't even move</i>

00:17:02.924 --> 00:17:04.358 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>and Tsubasa is uncovered.</i>

00:17:05.693 --> 00:17:08.128 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:17:08.161 --> 00:17:09.964 position:41% line:83% align:start
[girl]
Oh, no, my Misugi.

00:17:09.998 --> 00:17:11.533 position:30% line:83% align:start
Our dear prince
is full of mud.

00:17:11.566 --> 00:17:12.901 position:19% line:89% align:start
Is he going to be okay?

00:17:12.934 --> 00:17:14.067 position:35% line:89% align:start
Captain...

00:17:14.101 --> 00:17:16.203 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And here comes</i>
 <i>Musashi's defense.</i>

00:17:16.236 --> 00:17:17.337 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's your turn now, Teppei.

00:17:17.371 --> 00:17:18.840 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
It's mine now.

00:17:18.873 --> 00:17:20.107 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[yell]
-[grunt]

00:17:20.140 --> 00:17:22.109 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Seiji Kanda blocks</i>
 <i>Teppei Kisugi's shot.</i>

00:17:22.142 --> 00:17:23.243 position:35% line:83% align:start
It's mine.
[grunt]

00:17:23.277 --> 00:17:24.746 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Taki jumps</i>
 <i>to get the ball back.</i>

00:17:24.779 --> 00:17:25.880 position:16% line:89% align:start
I won't let you have it.

00:17:25.914 --> 00:17:28.115 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But Sanada</i>
 <i>from Musashi interferes.</i>

00:17:28.148 --> 00:17:29.751 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>Now Izawa has it</i>
-[grunt]

00:17:29.784 --> 00:17:30.885 position:27% line:83% align:start
- <i>and he shoots.</i>
-[grunt]

00:17:30.919 --> 00:17:32.085 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>And the goalie deflects</i>

00:17:32.119 --> 00:17:33.186 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>the shot with a fist.</i>

00:17:33.220 --> 00:17:34.421 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>Now Honma</i>
 <i>has the ball.</i>

00:17:34.454 --> 00:17:36.423 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Musashi shows off</i>
 <i>their magnificent defense.</i>

00:17:36.456 --> 00:17:38.325 position:10% line:83% align:start
-[Jun] Minoru, pass it here!
-Huh?

00:17:38.358 --> 00:17:39.426 position:38% line:89% align:start
Quickly!

00:17:39.459 --> 00:17:41.663 position:24% line:83% align:start
Minoru, I told you
to pass it.

00:17:41.696 --> 00:17:42.764 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yes, Captain.

00:17:43.463 --> 00:17:44.464 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's all yours.

00:17:44.498 --> 00:17:46.601 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And the ball</i>
 <i>goes directly to Misugi.</i>

00:17:46.634 --> 00:17:48.570 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Musashi gets ready</i>
 <i>for the counterattack.</i>

00:17:48.603 --> 00:17:49.202 position:38% line:89% align:start
Let's go.

00:17:50.170 --> 00:17:52.139 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Musashi's captain</i>
 <i>gets moving</i>

00:17:52.172 --> 00:17:53.908 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>at a great speed.</i>

00:17:53.942 --> 00:17:55.108 position:24% line:83% align:start
Everyone, come back
to defend.

00:17:55.142 --> 00:17:56.443 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm tired.</i>

00:17:56.476 --> 00:17:58.780 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I feel like my heart</i>
 <i>will burst out.</i>

00:18:00.048 --> 00:18:02.717 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Every step sends</i>
 <i>a sharp pain to my chest.</i>

00:18:02.750 --> 00:18:04.217 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's unbearable.</i>

00:18:04.752 --> 00:18:05.954 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>But...</i>

00:18:05.987 --> 00:18:09.824 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>as long as I can still feel</i>
 <i>the beating in my heart...</i>

00:18:09.857 --> 00:18:11.626 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>it means that I can still...</i>

00:18:11.659 --> 00:18:13.561 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>jump and shoot the ball.</i>

00:18:13.595 --> 00:18:19.567 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>My dad, my mom, Yayoi,</i>
 <i>Coach Isao, my friends...</i>

00:18:19.601 --> 00:18:23.037 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>All of you have helped me</i>
 <i>so much all this time.</i>

00:18:23.071 --> 00:18:24.171 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I feel so blessed.</i>

00:18:25.138 --> 00:18:28.275 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>And now, as the captain</i>
 <i>of Team Musashi,</i>

00:18:28.308 --> 00:18:30.177 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I can't disappoint you.</i>

00:18:30.210 --> 00:18:32.780 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll score a goal,</i>
 <i>even if it means my life.</i>

00:18:32.814 --> 00:18:33.514 position:19% line:83% align:start
-[ann] <i>Misugi is moving</i>
-Huh?

00:18:33.548 --> 00:18:34.481 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>faster and faster</i>
-No, no!

00:18:34.515 --> 00:18:35.717 position:27% line:83% align:start
- <i>with each step.</i>
-How did he

00:18:35.750 --> 00:18:36.851 position:24% line:89% align:start
get back his speed?

00:18:36.884 --> 00:18:38.118 position:19% line:89% align:start
Despite his condition,

00:18:38.151 --> 00:18:40.153 position:19% line:83% align:start
he's running way faster
than all of us.

00:18:40.187 --> 00:18:41.856 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I won't let him</i>
 <i>get any closer,</i>

00:18:41.889 --> 00:18:43.958 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll have to rely on</i>
 <i>any means.</i>

00:18:43.992 --> 00:18:45.158 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And Taro Misaki</i>
 <i>slide tackles</i>

00:18:45.192 --> 00:18:47.127 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>from the distance</i>
 <i>to take the ball away.</i>

00:18:47.160 --> 00:18:48.563 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>The water is letting him</i>
 <i>pick up speed.</i>

00:18:48.596 --> 00:18:49.731 position:21% line:89% align:start
You can do it, Taro.

00:18:49.764 --> 00:18:51.131 position:21% line:89% align:start
Be careful, Captain.

00:18:51.164 --> 00:18:54.434 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>Jump now.</i>
 <i>My body just has to jump.</i>

00:18:54.468 --> 00:18:55.435 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:18:55.469 --> 00:18:57.371 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Misugi jumps</i>
 <i>and evades Misaki.</i>

00:18:57.404 --> 00:18:59.406 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Taro] <i>The pitch is</i>
 <i>completely drenched.</i>

00:18:59.439 --> 00:19:01.709 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>How did he jump that high</i>
 <i>into the air?</i>

00:19:01.743 --> 00:19:03.176 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And here comes</i>
 <i>Shingo Takasugi,</i>

00:19:03.210 --> 00:19:04.311 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Team Nankatsu's defender.</i>

00:19:04.344 --> 00:19:06.246 position:16% line:83% align:start
You won't get through me,
your highness.

00:19:06.279 --> 00:19:09.917 position:13% line:83% align:start
Jun, look! Be careful with
the player on your left.

00:19:09.951 --> 00:19:11.284 position:38% line:83% align:start
-My son!
-My son!

00:19:11.318 --> 00:19:12.954 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ah!
-[ann] <i>Misugi loses</i>

00:19:12.987 --> 00:19:13.855 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>his balance.</i>
-It's mine.

00:19:13.888 --> 00:19:15.523 position:41% line:89% align:start
Misugi!

00:19:15.923 --> 00:19:17.125 position:47% line:89% align:start
Aw!

00:19:17.157 --> 00:19:19.259 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And he immediately</i>
 <i>extends his legs.</i>

00:19:19.292 --> 00:19:20.962 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>He's not letting</i>
 <i>anyone steal his ball.</i>

00:19:20.995 --> 00:19:22.262 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:19:22.295 --> 00:19:23.798 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Takasugi</i>
 <i>falls to the floor,</i>

00:19:23.831 --> 00:19:26.968 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Misugi has shown to have</i>
 <i>incredible will power.</i>

00:19:27.001 --> 00:19:28.301 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Now let's see if</i>
 <i>he can shoot</i>

00:19:28.335 --> 00:19:31.105 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>before Nankatsu's Captain</i>
 <i>manages to block him.</i>

